		<content type="html" xml:base="https://forums.sandboxie.com/phpBB3/viewtopic.php?t=15937&amp;p=91505#p91505"><![CDATA[
As the title says. Every time I update Sandboxie I have to re-adjust the Wacom Tablet template so it actually works with pressure sensitivity.<br><br>Current:<div class="codebox"><p>CODE: </p><pre><code>[Template_WacomTablet]Tmpl.Title=Wacom TabletTmpl.Class=DesktopTmpl.Url=http://www.wacom.com/customercare/drivers.aspxOpenIpcPath=\BaseNamedObjects\Wacom*WintabConnection*OpenIpcPath=$:Tablet.exe Tmpl.Scan=i</code></pre></div>Actually working:<div class="codebox"><p>CODE: </p><pre><code>[Template_WacomTablet]Tmpl.Title=Wacom TabletTmpl.Class=DesktopTmpl.Url=http://www.wacom.com/customercare/drivers.aspxOpenIpcPath=*\BaseNamedObjects*\Wacom*WintabConnection*   &lt;-- IMPORTANTOpenIpcPath=$:Tablet.exe Tmpl.Scan=i</code></pre></div>Could you adjust the default template to be functional for future updates? <img class="smilies" src="./../../.https://forums.sandboxie.com/phpBB3/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" width="15" height="15" alt=":)" title="Smile"><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.sandboxie.com/phpBB3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=16059">Domochevsky</a> — Thu Jul 04, 2013 6:59 pm</p><hr />
